            <h3 style="color: #667eea; margin-top: 0;">Vision</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>To be a globally recognized center of excellence in computer science education and research.</li>
                <li>To develop innovative solutions to real-world computing challenges.</li>
                <li>To nurture skilled professionals who contribute meaningfully to society.</li>
                <li>To foster an environment of continuous learning and technological advancement.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="color: #667eea;">Mission</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide high-quality education in computer science with emphasis on both theory and practice.</li>
                <li>Conduct cutting-edge research in emerging areas of computing.</li>
                <li>Develop graduates with strong technical skills, ethical values, and leadership qualities.</li>
                <li>Maintain strong collaborations with industry and academic institutions.</li>
                <li>Support the professional development of our faculty and staff.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

